{"tid":532064,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"MK恩曾自爆係「兵」迷","createTime":"2018-01-17T12:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T12:54:55.000Z","uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"457436f7d6daaf46c4c2a99a66095672bfe6dbd8","tid":532064,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:28:49.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=LsNY3Pycq2juKxw%2BplhkMTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=96ffdcea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】盛傳被曼聯用作與阿仙奴交易條件的米希達利恩，9年前原來曾在訪問裡指，最愛的球隊是阿仙奴，希望未來能夠為雲加效力。MK恩快將夢想成真嗎？<br />\n<br />\n即將過29歲生日的曼聯中場米希達利恩（Henrikh Mkhitaryan），近日成為英超轉會焦點人物之一，有媒體就找出他多年前的舊訪問，發現驚人真相！<br />\n<br />\n話說MK恩2009年仍然效力母會佩歷克的時候，曾經接受歐洲足協官網訪問，當時他透露，阿仙奴原來是其愛隊：「我最喜愛的球隊是阿仙奴。我喜歡他們的進攻及快速節奏；而且，領隊雲加要求球員踢出成績的同時，亦對年青球員十分信任。我很喜歡這樣，希望有一天能夠在那裡踢波。」<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，曼聯十分希望從引入阿仙奴的智利翼鋒阿歷斯山齊士，而MK恩是當中的交易籌碼；MK仔的經理人拉奧拿甚至公開承認，紅魔要簽入山齊士，基本上取決於MK恩的意願。<br />\n<br />\n不過，MK恩至今仍未答應成為兩間球會交易的一部份，有指這位阿美尼亞國腳或許對阿仙奴的前景不樂觀，因此感到猶豫。"},{"pid":"a6668710ac2661400be97649eb5494728034d2ae","tid":532064,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"9年前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://arsenalcolumn.files.wordpress.com/2008/08/arsenal-squad-2-copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farsenalcolumn.files.wordpress.com%2F2008%2F08%2Farsenal-squad-2-copy.jpg&h=050fb286&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ceae3c28304987df224a061d452e3231806e88b9","tid":532064,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"佢係兵迷 可能係原因令佢唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個勢唔對路  一堆人走佬"},{"pid":"54400e2b90e34dfb8112fd1bdf180d0de365a09f","tid":532064,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a6668710ac2661400be97649eb5494728034d2ae","tid":532064,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"9年前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://arsenalcolumn.files.wordpress.com/2008/08/arsenal-squad-2-copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farsenalcolumn.files.wordpress.com%2F2008%2F08%2Farsenal-squad-2-copy.jpg&h=050fb286&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"Billong原來係song<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a31f1f151dfc4a38f8e6e1a856cc55d85f47fcd","tid":532064,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54400e2b90e34dfb8112fd1bdf180d0de365a09f","tid":532064,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a6668710ac2661400be97649eb5494728034d2ae","tid":532064,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"9年前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://arsenalcolumn.files.wordpress.com/2008/08/arsenal-squad-2-copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farsenalcolumn.files.wordpress.com%2F2008%2F08%2Farsenal-squad-2-copy.jpg&h=050fb286&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"Billong原來係song<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:51:17.000Z","msg":"Alexandre Song Billong"},{"pid":"53760f60fc34e4c32c33d5d87c73325400e13186","tid":532064,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"希比唔係呢個時期咩"}]}